          <from>HON. ROSS LANDRY</from>
          <p>HON. ROSS LANDRY : Mr. Speaker, as Chairman of the Committee on Law Amendments, I am directed to report that the committee has met and considered the following bill:</p>
        </speech>
        <speech by="#75109949-5b99-4b9c-b9fd-d85a8ce227ab">
          <from>MR. SPEAKER</from>
          <p>MR. SPEAKER : Ordered that this bill be referred to the Committee of the Whole House on Bills.</p>
        </speech>
